<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.1">
<l>karuppūra nāṟumō kamalappū nāṟumō</l>
<l>tiruppavaḷac cevvāytāṉ tittit tirukkumō</l>
<l>maruppocitta mātavaṉṟaṉ vāyccuvaiyu nāṟṟamum</l>
<l>viruppuṟṟuk kēṭkiṉṟēṉ collāḻi veṇcaṅkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Does [His mouth] smell [like] camphor? [Or] does [it] smell [like] the lotus flower?</l>
<l>Are [His] sacred coral red lips sweet?</l>
<l>I am asking [you] with desire about the taste and the frangrance of the lips</l>
<l>of Mādhava, who broke the elephant tusk: tell [me], O white conch from the ocean!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
